&lt;br /&gt;
Not much is recorded about the life of Parikshit. &amp;nbsp;We only know about how he died, and the many snakes and Rishis who were involved in the process.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
So, I'm not quite through yet!&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5100791158359408086-2848744756486318606?l=mahabharatapodcast.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
