&lt;br /&gt;
The Pandavas then take a final tour of India, visiting even the former site of the magical city of Dwarka. &amp;nbsp;Finally, they head north, for Heaven, with their little dog Dharma.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5100791158359408086-3113977352649242311?l=mahabharatapodcast.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
