&lt;br /&gt;
Balaram shows up just in time to referee the final death match between Bhima &amp;amp; Duryodhana, only to get really annoyed when Bhima is forced to bend the rules a bit in order to win.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5100791158359408086-7525962334770064998?l=mahabharatapodcast.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
