t is time for one of Krishna's tricks!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Following Jayadratha's "exploding head syndrome", the Kauravas are so bent out of shape that they ignore the sunset and just keep fighting. &amp;nbsp; Next episode will cover the night battle of the 14th day.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
