&lt;br /&gt;
Also, the story is getting interesting.&amp;nbsp; We've got a few good fight scenes, plus Vyasa intervenes a couple of times to keep the story on track, and we get to meet Krishna for the first time!&amp;nbsp; By the end, we have our heroes married off to Draupadi and enjoying their honeymoon at King Drupada's palace.&amp;nbsp; We'll leave them to enjoy that for a while, and in the upcoming episodes, I'll go back in time to cover Krishna's story from the start. &lt;br /&gt;
